  <title>APC 维护屏幕</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading2">APC 维护屏幕</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">APC 有两种类型：</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="upper-alpha" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;">气动驱动</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal">伺服-M 驱动</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">根据 APC 类型，在机床上应用正确的 APC 维护屏幕，<text style="font-weight:bold;">3A - 气动驱动 </text>或 <text style="font-weight:bold;">3B - 伺服-M 驱动</text>。</para>
  </body>
